# Licensing

This repository contains multiple DCC add-ons with **per-folder licenses**:

| Folder | License | Notes |
|--------|---------|--------|
| `blender/` | **GPL-3.0-or-later** | Required for Blender add-ons (Blender API) |
| `unity/` | **MIT** | |
| `unreal/` | **MIT** | |

See `LICENSE` in each folder for full text.

**Motifect Motion is free.** Motion generation requires a [motifect.io](https://motifect.io) account, API key, and paid credits (cloud API).

Marketplace submission notes: [MARKETPLACE.md](MARKETPLACE.md)
